metadata.description:
«Entropy» is an illustration of the struggle between inevitable entropy and structured systems. The image of the face on one of the blocks denotes the key role of the person in the fight against the chaos. Entropy approaches ordered structures and recedes, but its danger is great.

Content specifications:
•	resolution 2480x3508px;
•	2d, handpaint (Adobe Photoshop);
•	animation (Adobe After Effects);
•	sound track;
•	60 FPS;
•	mp4 (47,5Mb).
